window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>Fear. Desire. Redemption.</i></b></p> <p>When I was taken...it changed me.</p> <p>Once, I was the life of the party. Not anymore.</p> <p>I told myself that I was okay. I almost believed it, until the day I was forced to face my past and my nightmare came to life.</p> <p>Now the Four are the only ones I can turn to, and Cassius Drummond has made it his personal mission to help me out.</p> <p>No matter how much I tell myself that he’s off-limits, the more time we spend together, the more I want him.</p> <p>Bound by my past, I know I’m no good for him, and I’m nothing more than a convenient distraction while we’re stuck with each other.</p> <p>It’s going to end in heartbreak.</p> <p>But every time he smiles at me, I find myself falling a little bit more. </p> <p><i>The Bonds We Break</i> is a stand-alone mature new-adult romance but is best enjoyed after the previous four books in the series.</p>"; 
